<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>Your details have been passed to me by&nbsp;<b>{!Lead.Partner_External_Name__c}&nbsp;</b>so that I can provide a quote for your required business insurance.<br><br>I haven’t yet been able to speak with you to provide your business insurance quote over the phone.&nbsp;<b>Is there a good time for me to try you again?<br></b><b><br></b>Here at Kingsbridge we offer a complete package of cover that is designed specifically for UK businesses. Our comprehensive package includes&nbsp;<b>Professional Indemnity</b>,&nbsp;<b>Public Liability</b>,&nbsp;<b>Employers’ Liability</b>,&nbsp;<b>Personal Accident</b>, and&nbsp;<b>Directors’ and Officers’ Liability</b>.&nbsp;<br><br>We can also include optional benefits such as:</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Cyber Liability&nbsp;</b>- Covers your business from risks related to your technology and IT infrastructure.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>IR35 Protect</b>&nbsp;- Protects limited company contractors from the potentially crippling costs that can follow an IR35 enquiry.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Legal Expenses</b>&nbsp;- Protects your business in the event of legal action.</font></li></ul><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>As a client of</b><b>&nbsp;</b><b>{!Lead.Partner_External_Name__c}<font color="#080707"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span></font></b><b>you are entitled to a discount&nbsp;</b></font><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">on our standard business insurance package.</b></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><b></b></p><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br>So, I can discuss with you which parts of the policy would be relevant for your business, it would be great to speak over the phone.&nbsp;<b>When would be a good time for me to reach you?<br></b><b><br></b>Alternatively, you can contact me on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<br><br>You can also get a quote online via our website&nbsp;<a href="http://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/">www.kingsbridge.co.uk</a>.<br><br>I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;<br><br><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}<br>Sales Team<br><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br>T:&nbsp;01242 808740</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>